---
apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1
kind: ClusterRole
metadata:
  name: pod-reader-all

rules:
- apiGroups: [""]
  resources: ["pods"]
  verbs: ["get","list","watch"]

---

apiVersion: rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1
kind: ClusterRoleBinding
metadata:
  name: global-pod-access

subjects:
- kind: User
  name: developer-user
  apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io

roleRef:
  kind: ClusterRole
  name: pod-reader-all
  apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io
---

Role            → Namespace permissions
RoleBinding     → Assign namespace permissions

ClusterRole     → Whole cluster permissions
ClusterRoleBinding → Assign cluster permissions
